<h1>Hearing Preparation</h1>
<p><strong>{{brand_name}}</strong> - {{claim_label}}</p>

<hr>

<h2>Core points to be ready to explain</h2>
<ol>
  {{#each legal_rules.required_elements}}
  <li>{{this}}</li>
  {{/each}}
</ol>

<h2>Claim summary</h2>
<p>{{claim_summary}}</p>

<h2>Evidence bundle</h2>
<p>
  Prepare a bundle that follows the Evidence Index. Put documents in date order where possible and make
  sure names, dates, amounts, and messages are readable.
</p>

{{#if evidence_rows.length}}
<ul>
  {{#each evidence_rows}}
  <li>{{label}} - {{description}}</li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>
{{/if}}

<h2>Hearing checklist</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Particulars of Claim checked against the evidence.</li>
  <li>Schedule of Loss totals checked.</li>
  <li>Copies of all key evidence available.</li>
  <li>Short chronology prepared.</li>
  <li>Notes prepared on attempts to resolve the dispute.</li>
</ul>
